    "media_text_YcUbbc": {
      "type": "media-text",
      "blocks": {
        "media_text_bg_4mk9kX": {
          "type": "media_text_bg",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/what-makes-us-better.webp",
            "heading": "Details Matter",
            "text": "<p>Settling just isn’t in our DNA. We chase the details that make a difference, from the character-rich stones we select to bricks with story built in. Even our packaging shows up looking like it means business. Everything we do is built to elevate your work, delivering masonry materials that install easily and look stunning. </p>",
            "button_text": "",
            "button_link": ""
          }
        },
        "media_text_bg_JMHLHY": {
          "type": "media_text_bg",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Creative_Mines_Team_Picture_1.webp",
            "heading": "A Rock-Solid Crew",
            "text": "<p>At Creative Mines, we are a group of passionate stone enthusiasts on a mission to elevate the art and science of masonry design.</p><p>Our masonry stone, brick, and architectural elements are crafted with unwavering attention to detail, blending artisan beauty with cutting-edge innovation.</p>",
            "button_text": "",
            "button_link": ""
          }
        },
        "media_text_bg_6fjJj8": {
          "type": "media_text_bg",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/whats-sets-us-apart.webp",
            "heading": "What Sets Us Apart",
            "text": "<p>Creative Mines is the <em>only</em> masonry veneer company incorporating 100% natural Pozzolan Pumice into its concrete mix design, delivering unmatched performance and longevity. The same material famously used in architectural icons like the Roman Colosseum.  </p><p>Pozzolan creates a tighter concrete matrix that eliminates common issues found within inferior manufactured stone, such as color fading, efflorescence, and stone degradation. </p><p>Why settle for anything less than legendary.</p>",
            "button_text": "",
            "button_link": ""
          }
        }
      },
