      "name": "Text with Icons",
      "settings": {
        "heading": "Responsibility, it’s what makes us better. ",
        "description": "<p>Masonry veneer should not only be suitable for deserving architectural styles, but respectful of the environment. We get that. That's why our products are designed with sustainability in mind and can contribute to earning LEED-certified points in several key categories. Our products are completely recyclable, reduce waste, reduce carbon footprint compared to clay brick and contribute to the reduction of natural stone excavation around the world.</p>"
      }
